PrefabInstance:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  serializedVersion: 2
  m_Modification:
    serializedVersion: 3
    m_TransformParent: {fileID: 0}
    m_Modifications:
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: player
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1111635702}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: advisor
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1312307796}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: spawnPoint
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 270352592}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: victoryTheme
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 52d1f34ccc1d99c4b90178747ce9736c, type: 3}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: spawnInterval
      value: 0.6
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: startWaveButton
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 2132640288}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: victoriousScreen
      value: 
      objectReference: {fileID: 1854532243}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.size
      value: 10
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[0].advisorMessage
      value: "Welcome to the Eastern region, Commander. From now on this area will
        be both your training grounds and area of \u200B\u200Bresponsibility. Place
        some TR-X turrets first to see how things work."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[1].advisorMessage
      value: 'I believe you were told this back in the academy, but let me remind
        you the basics: your Reputation Points is something that you should always
        be aware of.  You lose them if the Enemy reaches the designated area and
        if you lose them all, you will be sent back to the academy to repeat entire
        theoretical couse.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[2].advisorMessage
      value: Over time the enemies will be tougher and might have Immunities to certain
        types of damage, such as Bullet Resistance or Explosion Resistance so make
        sure to use your Towers wisely or the enemies will walk right past them to
        your doom. Bulletproof enemies are going to appear soon so place some Artillery
        towers around.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[3].advisorMessage
      value: 'As you have noticed, Earth Defense Corps have granted you and many
        other newly trained Commanders access to multiple types of Towers, such as:
        Factory, Railgun and more. Factory will deploy armored vehicles that will
        move along the path and attack enemies on it, place one and see how it works.'
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[4].advisorMessage
      value: Enemies with the Explosion resistance are detected, explosions will
        not deal any harm to them. They shouldn't be much of a threat. Unless you
        only place towers with explosive damage.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[5].advisorMessage
      value: Hmm. This is strange, this shouldn't be happening. I am going to contact
        R&D department. Stay on high alert, Commander.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[6].advisorMessage
      value: Commander! The U.E.F is under attack! We get reports that the Legion
        has launched a full-scale attack on all sections of the front, but we are
        still trying to figure out how they  found out about this place. Hold your
        ground!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[7].advisorMessage
      value: They are using our Training bots as cannon fodders to cover their forces!
        "Viper" class light tanks detected, we need some serious firepower to hold
        them!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[8].advisorMessage
      value: T-190M2 tanks spotted, a very serious threat, watch out! They are really
        trying to breakthrough our defenses! It might sound unorthodox, but maybe
        place some cheap towers in front to bait enemy attacks and protect more valuable
        towers from the attacks.
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[9].advisorMessage
      value: Commander, the scanner just lit up like a christmas tree! They are sending
        everything they've got to break through our defenses! HOLD THE LINE!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[0].advisorDuration
      value: 12
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[10].advisorMessage
      value: Commander! They are sending in their strongest armoured unit! Analyzes
        show that it is resistant to most of the bullets and only Explosions and
        our own armour can manage to take it down. Not to mention those 380mm cannons
        that can obliterate our forces. Do everything you can to take it down!
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 1548365845943686520, guid: 0fe81e41563ecf64ab0bc0c0ff9be323, type: 3}
      propertyPath: waves.Array.data[1].advisorDuration
      value: 15
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
